Python Level 1 & 2
==================

To get started you need to enter commands at your command prompt:

1. Load Python and Jupyter Notebook:

    module load python/3.7

2. Get the example notebook files from github:

    mkdir python_course
    cd python_course
    git clone https://github.com/seddon-software/python-notebooks.git

3. Open the folder with the downloaded notebooks

    cd python-notebooks

4. (Optional) To setup Juypter styles:

    ./setup.sh

5. Fire up Jupyter Notebook:

    jupyter notebook


